libsaxsdocument
===============
 * doxygen docs
 * language bindings: Fortran, C++, Python(?)
 * more formats
 * more testcases

libsaxsview
===========
 * doxygen docs

saxsview
========
 * save/restore last working directory
 * watch files for changes
 * allow for probability curves
 * if a .pdb-file shall be openend, run crysol 
   to display its scattering pattern
 * unified and simple way to export to .svg, .eps, .pdf, .jpg, etc
 * allow for annotations, e.g. freely placeable labels,
   on the plot area
 * configurable plot layout (see below)


Configurable Items in saxsview
------------------------------
All fonts shall individually be configurable in family, 
size and style (bold, italic).

Color selection should allow alpha channels.

Plot
 o palette
 o plot title
 o enable/disable (0/0) marker

Curves
 o lines (style, width, color)
 o symbols (type, size, color, filled)
 o error bars (style, width, color)
 o legend label
 o scaling factor (x-axis)
 o offset (y-axis)

For each axis
 o enable/disable axis label
 o axis label
 o axis label font

Ticks
 o enable/disable ticks
 o enable/disable tick labels
 o tick values (at least: from, to, spacing)
 o tick label font

Legend
 o enable/disable legend completely
 o legend font
 o legend position (?)

Grid (?)
 o enable/disable grid
 o grid spacing
 o grid line style

Other
 o annotation font
 o save default settings for new plots/curves (?)
